seo: 帆软报表,任意文件覆盖,文件上传,V9,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测帆软报表 V9 中存在的任意文件覆盖和文件上传漏洞，攻击者可能利用此漏洞覆盖关键文件（如/WebReport/a.svg.jsp）。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the arbitrary file overwrite and upload vulnerabilities in FineReport V9. Attackers may exploit this vulnerability to overwrite critical files (e.g., /WebReport/a.svg.jsp).
